Subject: Re: [VB] Backfire Problem

Look for intake leaks.

You can spray carb cleaner (not brake cleaner) at likely places for 
leaks like where the manifold bolts to the head and on the boots if it's 
a dual port engine. If the engine speeds up a little, you know there's a 
leak where you sprayed.

John

